---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Treatment Programs â€” Southern Winds Hospital" hideFooterCta>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg">
      <img src="/images/admissions-hero.png" alt="" loading="eager" />
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero__diagonal"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__curve"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <div class="page-hero__content">
        <h1 class="page-hero__heading">Treatment Programs</h1>
        <nav class="page-hero__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <span>/</span>
          <span aria-current="page">Programs</span>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="intro__inner">
      <div class="intro__content">
        <p>At Southern Winds Hospital, we have multiple programs carefully designed to provide the best care and assistance to our patients. Each treatment plan details a personal roadmap created by certified psychiatrists.</p>
        <p>Using an individualized treatment plan, we combine medical care with careful attention to one's daily routine and support system. With this level of care and attention, we achieve a healing process that is as nonintrusive as possible and that the patient remains willing to follow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="programs-section">
    <div class="programs-section__inner">

      <article class="program-card" id="inpatient">
        <div class="program-card__image">
          <img src="https://www.med.unc.edu/psych/wp-content/uploads/sites/839/2024/01/WMD_Inpatient.jpg" alt="Inpatient care at Southern Winds Hospital" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="program-card__content">
          <div class="program-card__badge">24/7 Supervised Care</div>
          <h2 class="program-card__title">Inpatient Program</h2>
          <p class="program-card__text">The Inpatient Program is the most intensive of all our programs. It consists of a complete accompaniment and is aimed at patients who need specialized, 24-hour supervision (for example, patients at risk of hurting themselves).</p>
          <p class="program-card__text">This program offers a safe and supervised environment. This program not only prevents interference with the recovery process but also stimulates and promotes progress through the qualified interaction provided by our team of professionals.</p>
          <ul class="program-card__features">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              24-hour professional supervision
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Safe and secure environment
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Individualized treatment plans
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Qualified psychiatric care team
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="program-card__btn">
            Learn More
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="program-card program-card--reverse" id="partial">
        <div class="program-card__image">
          <img src="https://www.med.unc.edu/psych/wp-content/uploads/sites/839/2024/01/WMD_Inpatient.jpg" alt="Partial Hospitalization Program" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="program-card__content">
          <div class="program-card__badge">Day Treatment</div>
          <h2 class="program-card__title">Partial Hospitalization Program (PHP)</h2>
          <p class="program-card__text">The Partial Hospitalization Program provides structured treatment during the day while allowing patients to return home in the evenings. This program is ideal for those who need intensive support but have a stable home environment.</p>
          <p class="program-card__text">Patients participate in group therapy, individual counseling, medication management, and skill-building activities throughout the day.</p>
          <ul class="program-card__features">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Structured daytime programming
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Return home each evening
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Group and individual therapy
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Medication management
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="program-card__btn">
            Learn More
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="program-card" id="iop">
        <div class="program-card__image">
          <img src="https://www.med.unc.edu/psych/wp-content/uploads/sites/839/2024/01/WMD_Inpatient.jpg" alt="Intensive Outpatient Program" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="program-card__content">
          <div class="program-card__badge">Flexible Schedule</div>
          <h2 class="program-card__title">Intensive Outpatient Program (IOP)</h2>
          <p class="program-card__text">The Intensive Outpatient Program offers a flexible treatment option for patients who need ongoing support while maintaining work, school, or family responsibilities.</p>
          <p class="program-card__text">Sessions are scheduled several times per week, providing consistent therapeutic support while allowing patients to practice new skills in their daily lives.</p>
          <ul class="program-card__features">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Flexible scheduling options
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Maintain daily responsibilities
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Multiple sessions per week
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Real-world skill application
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="program-card__btn">
            Learn More
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="program-card program-card--reverse" id="crisis">
        <div class="program-card__image">
          <img src="https://www.med.unc.edu/psych/wp-content/uploads/sites/839/2024/01/WMD_Inpatient.jpg" alt="Crisis Stabilization Unit" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="program-card__content">
          <div class="program-card__badge">Emergency Care</div>
          <h2 class="program-card__title">Crisis Stabilization Unit</h2>
          <p class="program-card__text">Our Crisis Stabilization Unit provides immediate, short-term care for individuals experiencing acute psychiatric emergencies. This program focuses on rapid stabilization and assessment.</p>
          <p class="program-card__text">Our experienced crisis team works quickly to ensure patient safety while developing an appropriate treatment plan for ongoing care.</p>
          <ul class="program-card__features">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Immediate intervention
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Rapid stabilization
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Comprehensive assessment
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Transition planning
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="program-card__btn">
            Learn More
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="levels-section">
    <div class="levels-section__inner">
      <h2 class="levels-section__heading">Levels of Care</h2>
      <p class="levels-section__subtext">Our programs are designed to meet you at every stage of your recovery journey.</p>
      <div class="levels-grid">
        <div class="level-card">
          <div class="level-card__number">1</div>
          <h3 class="level-card__title">Crisis Stabilization</h3>
          <p class="level-card__text">Immediate, short-term care for acute emergencies</p>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card__arrow">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card">
          <div class="level-card__number">2</div>
          <h3 class="level-card__title">Inpatient</h3>
          <p class="level-card__text">24/7 supervised care in a secure environment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card__arrow">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card">
          <div class="level-card__number">3</div>
          <h3 class="level-card__title">Partial Hospitalization</h3>
          <p class="level-card__text">Structured day treatment, home evenings</p>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card__arrow">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="level-card">
          <div class="level-card__number">4</div>
          <h3 class="level-card__title">Intensive Outpatient</h3>
          <p class="level-card__text">Flexible treatment while maintaining daily life</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-section__inner">
      <h2 class="cta-section__heading">Find the Right Program for You</h2>
      <p class="cta-section__text">Our admissions team will help determine which level of care best meets your needs.</p>
      <div class="cta-section__actions">
        <a href="tel:7868267552" class="cta-section__btn cta-section__btn--primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
          Call (786) 826-7552
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-section__btn cta-section__btn--secondary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/partials/variables' as *;
  @use '../styles/partials/mixins' as *;

  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 220px;
    overflow: hidden;

    @include respond(md) {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    &__bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 1;

      img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      &::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba($color-primary, 0.75);
      }
    }

    &__diagonal {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 60%;
      height: 100%;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 70% 100%, 0 100%);
      z-index: 2;

      @include respond(md) {
        width: 50%;
        clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 65% 100%, 0 100%);
      }
    }

    &__curve {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 50px;
      background: $color-white;
      z-index: 4;
      clip-path: ellipse(45% 100% at 50% 100%);

      @include respond(md) {
        height: 70px;
        clip-path: ellipse(45% 100% at 50% 100%);
      }
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      padding-block: $space-2xl;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;

      @include respond(lg) {
        padding-block: $space-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-white;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;

      &::after {
        content: '';
        display: block;
        width: 48px;
        height: 3px;
        background-color: $color-white;
        margin-top: $space-xs;
      }

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: rgba($color-white, 0.85);
      margin-top: $space-xs;

      a {
        color: rgba($color-white, 0.85);
        transition: color $transition-fast;

        &:hover {
          color: $color-white;
        }
      }

      span[aria-current] {
        color: $color-white;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    }
  }

  .intro {
    background: $color-white;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;
    padding-top: $space-lg;

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    &__content {
      text-align: center;

      p {
        font-family: $font-body;
        font-size: $fs-sm;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: $color-text-muted;
        margin-bottom: $space-md;

        &:last-child {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        @include respond(md) {
          font-size: $fs-base;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .programs-section {
    background: $color-offwhite;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
    }
  }

  .program-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: $space-lg;
    margin-bottom: $space-2xl;
    background: $color-white;
    border-radius: $radius-lg;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: $shadow-md;

    &:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    @include respond(lg) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }

    &--reverse {
      @include respond(lg) {
        .program-card__image {
          order: 2;
        }
        .program-card__content {
          order: 1;
        }
      }
    }

    &__image {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      overflow: hidden;

      @include respond(lg) {
        aspect-ratio: auto;
        min-height: 400px;
      }

      img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform $transition-slow;
      }

      .program-card:hover & img {
        transform: scale(1.03);
      }
    }

    &__content {
      padding: $space-md;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;

      @include respond(lg) {
        padding: $space-2xl;
      }
    }

    &__badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: $space-xs $space-sm;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-xs;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: $color-primary;
      background: rgba($color-primary, 0.1);
      border-radius: $radius-full;
      margin-bottom: $space-sm;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    &__title {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      margin-bottom: $space-md;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-2xl;
      }
    }

    &__text {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: $color-text-muted;
      margin-bottom: $space-sm;

      &:last-of-type {
        margin-bottom: $space-md;
      }
    }

    &__features {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 $space-lg 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: $space-xs;

      @include respond(sm) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: $space-xs;
        font-family: $font-body;
        font-size: $fs-sm;
        color: $color-text;

        svg {
          color: $color-primary;
          flex-shrink: 0;
        }
      }
    }

    &__btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $space-xs;
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: $color-primary;
      width: fit-content;
      transition: gap $transition-base;

      &:hover {
        gap: $space-sm;
      }

      svg {
        transition: transform $transition-base;
      }

      &:hover svg {
        transform: translateX(3px);
      }
    }
  }

  .levels-section {
    background: $color-white;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;
    }

    &__subtext {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-sm;
      color: $color-text-muted;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: $space-xl;
    }
  }

  .levels-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: $space-md;

    @include respond(lg) {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: $space-sm;
    }
  }

  .level-card {
    background: $color-offwhite;
    border: 1px solid $color-border;
    border-radius: $radius-md;
    padding: $space-lg;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 240px;
    transition: all $transition-base;

    &:hover {
      border-color: $color-primary;
      box-shadow: $shadow-md;
    }

    &__number {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-lg;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-white;
      background: $color-primary;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: $space-sm;
    }

    &__title {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-base;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-navy;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;
    }

    &__text {
      font-family: $font-body;
      font-size: $fs-xs;
      color: $color-text-muted;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    &__arrow {
      color: $color-primary;
      display: none;

      @include respond(lg) {
        display: block;
      }
    }
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba($color-primary-dark, 0.52), rgba($color-primary, 0.88)), url('/images/waves.png') center / cover no-repeat;
    padding-block: $space-2xl;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;

    @include respond(lg) {
      padding-block: $space-3xl;
    }

    &__inner {
      @include container;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    &__heading {
      font-family: $font-heading;
      font-size: $fs-2xl;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: $color-white;
      margin-bottom: $space-xs;

      @include respond(md) {
        font-size: $fs-3xl;
      }
    }

    &__text {
